    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, providing a confident driving experience. The transmission shifts are crisp and dependable, with no signs of slipping or hesitation. While it shows some very minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and the exterior paint retains a nice luster. All major systems, including the climate control and electronics, are fully functional. This is a solid, well-cared-for car that is ready for many more miles of service.",
