    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips between gears. The body shows heavy wear with noticeable rust, dents, and fading paint, while the interior requires a complete overhaul due to tears and stains. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a valuable source for parts.",
